# Credit connector coding

Before changing bill/open-cycle logic, read `docs/connectors/README.md` and the guide for the bank involved.

- Never use `account.balance` as open-bill total when it equals `creditLimit − availableCreditLimit` (total outstanding).
- Index by **due month**, not calendar purchase month.
- Deduplicate installment projections against real `PENDING`/`POSTED` with the same `N/M`.
- Keep `src/utils/creditConnectors/profiles.js` in sync with `docs/connectors/*.md`.
- Edge copy: `supabase/functions/pluggy-proxy/creditBillPeriod.ts` (+ `creditConnectors/`).
